Diamond Men;;58;;81;;R;;Eddie Miller (Robert Forster) has spent his life traversing the roads of Pennsylvania, selling diamonds and jewelry to small shops. After a heart attack makes him an insurance risk, his company informs Eddie that it's time he trains his replacement, Bobby Walker (Donnie Wahlberg), a coarse, brash young man with no sales experience. Despite their differences, the two become friends, and Bobby introduces Eddie to Tina (Jasmine Guy), a madam with a rough exterior but a heart of gold.;;Drama,Comedy;;Dan Cohen;;2001;;Robert Forster,Donnie Wahlberg,Bess Armstrong,Jasmine Guy,George Coe,Kristin Minter;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/diamond_men